title: Keisuke Matsumoto
text:
is a former <a href="Japanese%20people">Japanese</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
Playing career.
Keisuke Matsumoto played for <a href="MIO%20Biwako%20Shiga">MIO Biwako Shiga</a> and <a href="Grulla%20Morioka">Grulla Morioka</a> from 2011 to 2015.
